### 1. 헬스체크 (서버 실행 확인)
GET http://localhost:8081/health

###

### 2. 회원가입
POST http://localhost:8081/api/users/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tass@zoni.com",
  "password": "1234",
  "nickname": "tass"
}

###

### 3. 로그인 (accessToken + refreshToken 발급)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tass@zoni.com",
  "password": "1234"
}

###

### 4. 내 정보 조회 - 로그인 응답의 accessToken 복사해서 Bearer 뒤에 붙여넣기
GET http://localhost:8081/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ0YXNzQHpvbmkuY29tIiwidXNlcklkIjozLCJuaWNrbmFtZSI6InRhc3MiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzU3MjY1MTMsImV4cCI6MTc3NTcyODMxM30.gA62nUwteDv705Q886WTM0hBeBgkhbEpFGjsLUlrQPEyTZ1lzP5tShZeUUJIDjtO


###

### 5. Access Token 재발급 - 로그인 응답의 refreshToken 복사해서 붙여넣기
POST http://localhost:8081/api/users/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ0YXNzQHpvbmkuY29tIiwidXNlcklkIjozLCJuaWNrbmFtZSI6InRhc3MiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzU3MjYxNDEsImV4cCI6MTc3NjMzMDk0MX0.Bh-vgs1NO3Fvx2fbvFyPWfMzprATiFLq321cmtdKT8AilFdlf4cqgIi4F5ziOWDW"
}

###

### 6. 로그아웃 - accessToken 필요
POST http://localhost:8081/api/users/logout
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ0YXNzQHpvbmkuY29tIiwidXNlcklkIjozLCJuaWNrbmFtZSI6InRhc3MiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzU3MjYxNzcsImV4cCI6MTc3NTcyNzk3N30.TzkiU4SU9kACtvN2RWuy4xvnL6PWsz1RWmGVDo9YpBKDA18epaCIAhLrx5RmLaAN

###

### 7. 중복 이메일 테스트 (409 응답 확인)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/users/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tass@zoni.com",
  "password": "1234",
  "nickname": "tass"
}

###

### 8. 잘못된 비밀번호 테스트 (401 응답 확인)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tass@zoni.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}
